works.description: For that price, you could get yourself a brand new luxury car. But, if you are one of those who could spend a million dollars on a fishing lure or buy a $80,000 aquarium fish, you would love to know of this red dragon flour fish that costs 360,000 Yuan ($55,440 at the time of writing). Available at a shop in Chengdu, Sichuan province in China, this fish is 55cm long, weighs in at 1.5 kg and is imported from Indonesia.
